 Mana yanjye, Mana yanjye ni iki gitumye untererana?
 Byose... birarangiye.
 Data nshyize ubugingo bwanjye mu maboko yawe.
 Yesu apfa ahagana ku isaha ya cyenda z'umugoroba. Abasirikare bamutera icumu mu rubavu, havamo amazi n'amaraso.
 Ibyanclitswe byera biravuga ngo: Nk'umwana w'intama, yajyanywe mu ibagiro.
 Tujye gusaba umurambo we tuwuhambe.
 Yarakomerekejwe, yarashenjaguwe kubera ibyaha byacu. Noneho yarapfuye.
 Ese yari Mesiya wagombaga kuza?
 Yosefu wo mu Arimatayo na Niko demu bafata umurambo wa Yesu, bawusiga ibihumura, bawuhambira mu gitambaro gishya, nyuma bawu shyira mu mva ya Yozefu bayikingi sha igitare.
 Kuki mushakira umuzima mu bapfu ye? Yazutse. Nimugende mubibwire abigishwa.
 Ku wa mbere w'iminsi irindwi hari abagore bari mu gahinda, bajya ku mva.
 Eh! Urutare rwavuyeho!
